    <item>
      <title>米莱钦佩爱尔兰，但爱尔兰人并不喜欢其经济统计数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/milei-admires-ireland-for-an-economic-statistic-the-irish-don-t-favor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱伊 (Javier Milei) 希望以爱尔兰在过去 30 年扭转命运的方式改革阿根廷经济。爱尔兰人对自己的故事有更多细微的了解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/milei-admires-ireland-for-an-economic-statistic-the-irish-don-t-favor</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:56:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威金融监管机构认为房价可能大幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/norway-s-finance-watchdog-sees-risk-of-sharp-home-price-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威金融监管机构警告称，挪威是发达国家中家庭负债最高的国家，如果房价上涨，其银行可能面临更大的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/norway-s-finance-watchdog-sees-risk-of-sharp-home-price-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:50:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业前景：十一月报告值得关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/us-jobs-preview-what-to-watch-for-in-november-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国 11 月非农就业人数预计将从 10 月份的近零数字反弹，失业率可能会上升，因为下岗工人和新进入劳动力市场的人很难找到工作。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视上进行了预告。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/us-jobs-preview-what-to-watch-for-in-november-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:38:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 Advent 将为新的 250 亿美元基金招募投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/advent-is-said-to-canvass-investors-for-new-25-billion-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，收购公司 Advent 已开始为新的旗舰基金招募投资者，该基金的规模可能与其之前创纪录的 250 亿美元基金相似。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/advent-is-said-to-canvass-investors-for-new-25-billion-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:36:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基汇资本牵头集团将为收购香港中心大厦的贷款进行再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/gaw-capital-led-group-to-refinance-loan-used-to-buy-hk-tower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由香港基金管理公司基汇资本牵头的投资财团正在寻求一笔 54 亿港元（6.94 亿美元）的贷款，以再融资用于收购太古城中心一期办公大楼的债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/gaw-capital-led-group-to-refinance-loan-used-to-buy-hk-tower</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:23:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
