    <item>
      <title>奥尔班威胁称，除非匈牙利获得资金，否则将否决欧盟预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/orban-threatens-eu-budget-veto-unless-hungary-funds-are-released</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班威胁说，除非匈牙利重新获得欧盟因法治和腐败问题而冻结的资金，否则他将否决欧盟的下一份长期预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/orban-threatens-eu-budget-veto-unless-hungary-funds-are-released</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 08:21:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员关注美联储降息，关注就业数据以寻找线索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/bond-traders-leaning-on-fed-rate-cuts-eye-us-jobs-data-for-clues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员为押注美联储本月晚些时候降息寻求支持，他们将密切关注周五公布的美国 11 月份就业报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/bond-traders-leaning-on-fed-rate-cuts-eye-us-jobs-data-for-clues</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 01:23:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
